OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Truly remarkable' drug    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhelps motor neurone disease
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scientists say they have slowed and    
OL,6, even reversed some of the devastating  
OL,7, and relentless decline caused by       
OL,8, motor-neurone disease (MND).           
OL,10,FThe treatment works in only 2% of      
OL,11,Fpatients but has been described as     
OL,12,F"truly remarkable" and a "real moment  
OL,13,Fof hope" for the whole disease.        
OL,15,FOne leading expert said it was the     
OL,16,Ffirst time she had seen patients       
OL,17,Fimprove - but this is not a cure.      
OL,19,FThe MND Association said there was     
OL,20,F"mounting confidence" in the therapy.  
